WEBVTT

00:00.600 --> 00:01.160
The east

00:01.840 --> 00:03.400
Had smoke rising early

00:04.120 --> 00:04.840
While the west

00:05.440 --> 00:06.520
Only started cooking at dusk

00:07.360 --> 00:08.280
This shows the supervision troops

00:09.000 --> 00:10.360
Should have returned to the western camp

00:11.000 --> 00:11.560
These past few days

00:12.440 --> 00:14.520
The Wuzhao only sent Xuan people to die

00:14.840 --> 00:16.440
Mainly to exhaust our arrows

00:17.480 --> 00:18.640
And demoralize our troops

00:19.160 --> 00:19.960
Those supervising

00:20.760 --> 00:21.520
Should not be the main force

00:22.120 --> 00:23.000
So the enemy's main force

00:23.000 --> 00:23.840
Should be in the east

00:25.440 --> 00:25.800
Tonight

00:27.480 --> 00:28.360
Raid the western camp

00:29.280 --> 00:29.680
Brother-in-law

00:30.320 --> 00:31.480
I ask to lead the cavalry out of the city

00:32.120 --> 00:32.760
They are all

00:32.760 --> 00:33.760
Brothers who have followed me

00:34.160 --> 00:35.320
Since I joined the army

00:36.000 --> 00:37.040
Each willing to fight to the death
